Cook the pasta according to package directions and drain. Meanwhile, steam the cauliflower in a large saucepan until tender-crisp to your liking. Add the tomatoes, peas, and curry powder and bring to a simmer. Cook gently over medium-low heat, just until the mixture is heated through. Combine the pasta and cauliflower mixture in a serving container and toss together. Season with salt and serve. 3. Combine the pasta and cauliflower mixture in a serving container and toss together. Season with salt and serve.